#: src/Dialogs/dlgGestureHelp.cpp:16
msgid ""
"# Gesture Navigation\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n"
"\n"
"- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n"
"- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n"
"- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen "
"mode\n"
"- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n"
"- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n"
"- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n"
"- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n"
"- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n"
"- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n"
"- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n"
"- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n"
"- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan "
"mode\n"
"- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** "
"(LDRDL): Status\n"
"- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick "
"menu\n"
"\n"
"Long-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby "
"waypoints."
msgstr ""
"# Navigacija gestama\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar podržava pokrete dodirom na karti:\n"
"\n"
"- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Prevucite prema gore** (U): Povećajte\n"
"- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Povucite prema dolje** (D): Smanji\n"
"- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Prevucite udesno** (R): prethodni način "
"rada zaslona\n"
"- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Prevucite ulijevo** (L): Sljedeći način "
"rada zaslona\n"
"- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Gore-Dolje** (UD): Automatski zum\n"
"- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Dolje-gore** (DU): Izbornik\n"
"- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Dolje-desno** (DR): pojedinosti "
"međutočke\n"
"- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Dolje-lijevo** (DL): Zamjene\n"
"- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **desno-dolje** (RD): Upravitelj zadataka\n"
"- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Gore-desno-dolje** (URD): Analiza\n"
"- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Lijevo-dolje-desno** (LDR): popis za "
"provjeru\n"
"- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Gore-desno-dolje-lijevo** (URDL): "
"način pomicanja\n"
"- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Lijevo-dolje-desno-dolje-lijevo** "
"(LDDRL): Status\n"
"- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Gore-lijevo-dolje-desno** (ULDR): "
"Brzi izbornik\n"
"\n"
"Dugo pritisnite kartu za ulazak u način rada Pan. Dodirnite dok ste u načinu "
"Pan da biste vidjeli obližnje putne točke."

